video.title: Saturday Night Live: The 2010s
video.synopsis: "SNL" targets the future with sketches and skits featuring regulars like Fred Armisen, Seth Meyers, Andy Samberg, Jason Sudeikis and Kristen Wiig.

episodes.synopsis: After a debate among Republican presidential hopefuls, Alec Baldwin becomes the show's most frequent host, with walk-on assistance from Steve Martin.
episodes.title: Alec Baldwin/Radiohead

episodes.synopsis: After opening the show in a Lawrence Welk sendup, host Melissa McCarthy plays a love-struck office worker and a Mae West clone.
episodes.title: Melissa McCarthy/Lady Antebellum
